1. Project Overview

Project Name

Cognitive Tutor: One-Document â†’ Mastery

Theme

Theme 2: Reasoning and Personalized Experience (Maximized Context)

Problem Statement

Most AI learning tools rely on:

Shallow summarization

Repeated document reprocessing

Multi-turn conversations that waste tokens


As a result, they fail to measure true understanding, personalize learning, and scale efficiently.

Our Solution

Cognitive Tutor transforms any large document into a personalized learning experience using:

A single deep reasoning pass over the document

Complex, rubric-backed questions

Single-turn evaluation with personalized feedback


This enables deep comprehension, not just surface-level Q&A.


